  "title": "Kubernetes Security Advisories - 2023-07-26",
  "description": "Merged 2 kubernetes security advisories published on 2023-07-26. Original advisory IDs: CVE-2023-3955, CVE-2023-3893\n\nTitles:\n- Insufficient input sanitization on Windows nodes leads to privilege escalation\n- Insufficient input sanitization on kubernetes-csi-proxy leads to privilege escalation",
